{"tid":449613,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺TB係一個好奇怪既物種","createTime":"2017-10-27T10:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T15:33:19.000Z","uid":12370,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"610d687ced12f258277c88507decc37fd1f31590","tid":449613,"uid":12370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"今日番工遇到一個客<br />\n我就同佢講：先生想要咩野？<br />\n個客就西我面答我：我係小姐你係唔係特登叫錯架咁都睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頂你剪到成個勁短既油頭戴眼鏡著MK老西我點睇得出你男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係你額頭寫住我係女先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評：TB又要扮到成個男人咁但又唔俾人叫先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評：人地就算點著你都要睇得出佢有冇J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c9934bfc3bdec114bb2b8728387e6c15ef1ebb","tid":449613,"uid":85751,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"topic 好，但投你老母票咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bf2bf94d5c541d235b64ff728c1294cc1df42e","tid":449613,"uid":155591,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"TB剪頭髮有加乘  剛柔並重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過永遠只會叫佢地英文名<br />\n先生定小姐唔夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705e2931966d8286eba6d0de2a9f51c61ebfa3c","tid":449613,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TB剪頭髮有加乘  剛柔並重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過永遠只會叫佢地英文名<br />\n先生定小姐唔夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定嗌小姐<br />\n最多認錯乸型系女<br />\n但冇理由將呢D奇怪物種視為同類（I.e. 男人）"},{"pid":"c070e966c0621ee419b9d15e3a29c0fa2443c002","tid":449613,"uid":12370,"li